Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:14.12,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,950)\pos(140,435)\fsp5\blur2}红的极秘任务\N与第三代的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次任务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我展现这段时期学习成果的最佳时机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都陷入幻术了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云 是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了 八云
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先前进去的两个人还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来八云的能力渐渐觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去对付八云跟红
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让援兵前来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家纹是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是鞍马一族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕日红 乖乖把八云交出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们鞍马一族对八云有何企图
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的内部问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云是第三代委托给我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就休怪我无礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将计就计 让我们反陷入幻术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 别急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些豆子也太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳命来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻术是奈何不了虫子的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你躲起来 味道却消不掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兽人分身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙通牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木叶刚力旋风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种半调子的幻术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对久经考验的我们是无效的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 放开我 快放开我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你一头冲进敌人幻术里的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师跟八云
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:08:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们四个都中了幻术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没她们的踪影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候对我施的幻术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 居然解不开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是继我父亲过世后执掌鞍马一族的云海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞍马一族的云海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 难怪不容易对付
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻术忍者 夕日红
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能得到你的夸奖甚为荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你别做无谓的抗争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖把八云交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抱住我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便你是夕日红
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了我的幻术又如何跟我斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我会刺穿你的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把八云交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你伤害红老师的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:11:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 难道你不长记性吗 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人 敌人在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用幻术的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多重影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的分身可不是幻术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人连弹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放弃八云的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚让八云吃了点安神的药
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最好还是带她回村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做一个详细的检查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸亏有你帮忙 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 你也得赶紧接受治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看你的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几个家伙一直都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他们暂时无法从幻术中清醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来还不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经做了紧急处理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过伤口很深
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须赶紧回村才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云情绪不稳 反而让我比较担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的同伙估计还会返回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护八云的三个人没了踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人放心不下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这里就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们和红一起带着八云回村
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再带增援部队前来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是幻术忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应付得来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体可是久经锻炼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:14:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会被鞍马一族那种小幻术给蒙骗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为红老师封印了你的幻术能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你怀恨在心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她打从心底里讨厌我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不希望我成为一名幻术忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你误会老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她这么做一定有她的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才如果不是红老师冒死营救你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就要被人掳走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:15:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是鞍马一族 我的族人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同族人为什么要这么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙 你可以带红老师回村吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事 自己能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师 请告诉我们真相
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你不肯执教我们班有关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云所在的鞍马一族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是以傲视群雄的幻术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占据木叶重要地位的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但近年来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为培养不出上忍 中忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以家道中落
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这时出现了一颗希望之星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是八云
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母和亲戚都把希望寄托在宗家的独生女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是从小身体虚弱的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法正式就读忍者学校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背负着双亲和族人希望的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷入了绝望的深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不忍看我难过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是去找第三代火影大人求情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟丛云交流后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三代发现了八云的优秀潜力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便打算交由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第三代火影大人的命令下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师开始给我特训
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师她…红老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许同为幻术忍者的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒八云那种优秀的潜能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里不需要比我更厉害的幻术忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 老师怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这种自私的人 怎么配带领你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对木叶而言 我也是眼中钉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师应该有所隐瞒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要问为何的话 在回忆往事时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师的手颤抖不止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在讲述动机时 手却停止了颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个动机是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是谎言 心就不会动摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她嫉妒八云也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师应该是在为某人打掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师想掩护的人 比如…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红老师跟第三代火影大人的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样八云短期内能力就不会觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水决堤溢出的时候早晚会来临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞍马一族的力量早晚会威胁到木叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时 我们就不得不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的能力遭到封印
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对和第三代火影大人有关
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三代是不可能下达这种命令的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟红老师修炼没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一场突如其来的火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火势迅速蔓延 根本无法救援
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父母都是上忍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能死于一场白天的火灾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事后 一方面告知这是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一方面却把验尸报告作为秘密封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非不是单纯的火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母会死也是因为第三代的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 这决不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.01,0:22:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的话 红老师的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.99,0:22:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底谁真谁假
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.03,0:22:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们都不像在骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有一件事我很确定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三代爷爷决不可能想除掉姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.14,0:22:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当务之急
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.25,0:22:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是带老师她们回医院治疗…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:22:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻觉或真实 控制五感的人